==職業生涯==
===小聯盟時期===
諾瓦是在2004年和[[紐約洋基|紐約洋基]]簽下合約。在小聯盟體系裡面，一直到2008年結束，諾瓦還沒有升到2A，之後就經由規則五選秀（Rule 5 draft）被[[聖地牙哥教士|聖地牙哥教士]]選走<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://sandiego.padres.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20081211&content_id=3713424&vkey=pr_sd&fext=.jsp&c_id=sd|title=Padres select infielder Everth Cabrera and right-handed pitcher Ivan Nova in Rule 5 Draft|publisher=Sandiego.padres.mlb.com|date=2008-12-11|accessdate=2010-05-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218112040/http://sandiego.padres.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20081211&content_id=3713424&vkey=pr_sd&fext=.jsp&c_id=sd|archivedate=2008-12-18}}</ref>。在2009年春訓結束以後，被教士給放棄，諾瓦又再度回到洋基<ref>{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Krasovic|url=http://www3.signonsandiego.com/weblogs/padres/2009/mar/29/padres-moving-burke-out/|title="Padres trade Burke to Mariners" by Padres Scorecard|publisher=signonsandiego.com|date=2009-03-29|accessdate=2010-05-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522174113/http://www.signonsandiego.com/weblogs/padres/2009/mar/29/padres-moving-burke-out/|archivedate=2010-05-22}}</ref>。這是因為在春訓的表現不佳，在8.2局的投球中，被擊出13支安打失8分，防禦率高達8.31<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090329&content_id=4086436&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Padres return Nova to Yankees: San Diego had selected the right-hander in December's Rule 5 Draft|first=Bryan|last=Hoch|work=MLB.com|date=2009-03-29|accessdate=2010-08-23|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221221832/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090329&content_id=4086436&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb}}</ref>。2009年，諾瓦先從小聯盟2A開始，球季中升到3A<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091122&content_id=7702382&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy|title=Yanks' homegrown talent often overlooked: Contribution to Series title most recognizable in bullpen|first=Jonathan|last=Mayo|work=MLB.com|date=2009-11-24|accessdate=2010-08-23|archive-date=2014-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306073732/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091122&content_id=7702382&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy}}</ref>。在2009年球季結束以後，諾瓦被球隊放進40人名單中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://yankees.lhblogs.com/2009/11/20/seven-added-to-40-man-roster/ |title=Seven added to 40-man roster | The Lohud Yankees Blog |publisher=Yankees.lhblogs.com |date=2009-11-20 |accessdate=2010-05-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305031920/http://yankees.lhblogs.com/2009/11/20/seven-added-to-40-man-roster/ |archivedate=2010-03-05 }}</ref>，避免被其他球隊透過規則五選秀選走<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091208&content_id=7772728&vkey=hotstove2009&fext=.jsp|title=Cabrera star of '08 Rule 5 Draft: Padres' speedy shortstop has made an impact in Majors|first=Lisa|last=Winston|work=MLB.com|date=2009-12-08|accessdate=2010-08-23|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023061338/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091208&content_id=7772728&vkey=hotstove2009&fext=.jsp}}</ref>。2010年球季，諾瓦在小聯盟有優異的表現，6場先發中的防禦率只有2.43<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/37070044/sports/player_news |title=Deadlink |publisher=NBC Sports |work=nbcsports.com |date=2010-05-10 |accessdate=2010-08-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514063721/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/37070044/sports/player_news |archivedate=2010-05-14 }}</ref>。

===大聯盟時期===
2010年5月10日，諾瓦升上大聯盟，主要擔任[[長中繼|長中繼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.thetimes-tribune.com/yankees/?p=4337|title=Nova gets the call|publisher=Scranton Times-Tribune|work=Scranton/Wilkes-Barre Yankees Blog|date=2010-05-10|accessdate=2010-05-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100515135249/http://blogs.thetimes-tribune.com/yankees/?p=4337|archivedate=2010-05-15}}</ref>。之後在8月23日因[[哈維爾·巴斯克斯|哈維爾·巴斯克斯]]表現不佳，而取代之成為先發投手，並在8月29日面對芝加哥白襪的比賽中，以2：1獲勝，拿下大聯盟生涯的第1勝<ref>{{cite news|last=Sablich|first=Justin|url=http://bats.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/08/21/rodriguezs-long-term-status-remains-uncertain/|title=Rodriguez to Disabled List; Nova to Start Monday|work=Bats Blog - NYTimes.com|publisher=New York Times|date=2010-08-21|accessdate=2010-08-21|archive-date=2011-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727020625/http://bats.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/08/21/rodriguezs-long-term-status-remains-uncertain/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Bryan |last=Hoch |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100824&content_id=13862910&notebook_id=13862912&vkey=notebook_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy |title=Vazquez to 'pen for now; Nova up Sunday |publisher=MLB.com |date=2010-08-24 |accessdate=2010-08-25 |archive-date=2010-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100828201145/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100824&content_id=13862910&notebook_id=13862912&vkey=notebook_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy }}</ref>。

2011年由於諾瓦在春訓有優異的表現，而順利成為洋基先發投手一員<ref>{{cite web|title=Freddy Garcia makes Yanks' rotation|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/news/story?id=6260701|date=March 28, 2011|accessdate=2014-06-10|language=en|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701185731/http://sports.espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/news/story?id=6260701}}</ref>。
2011年球季結束諾瓦以16勝4敗3.70 ERA，勝場數僅次於[[卡斯坦·查爾斯·沙巴西亞|卡斯坦·查爾斯·沙巴西亞]]的19勝(8敗)，美聯分區賽第一戰因雨讓沙巴西亞逼不得已把第二戰的諾瓦上來中繼，主投6.1局只被打4支安打5K4BB失兩分拿下勝投，但是到了第五戰諾瓦只投兩局被打3支安打包含兩支全壘打3K最後吞下敗投。

2014年4月19日諾瓦對光芒隊因右手手肘受傷，被診斷為部分撕裂尺側副韌帶，可能需要[[湯米·約翰手術|湯米·約翰手術]]，也宣告本季報銷。

2016年8月1日，諾瓦被洋基交易到匹茲堡海盜換取另外兩名球員。

2018年12月11日，[[芝加哥白襪隊|芝加哥白襪隊]]為了補強輪值，透過交易送出右投手羅沙里歐（Yordi Rosario）與價值50萬的國際選秀簽約金給[[匹茲堡海盜隊|匹茲堡海盜隊]]換來諾瓦。<ref>[http://www.tsna.com.tw/tw/news/show.php?num=24029 白襪補強先發輪值　從海盜換來Nova] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tsna.com.tw/tw/news/show.php?num=24029 |date=20190802040814 }}，TSNA，2018-12-12</ref>

